<template><div><h1 id="rxjs-reactive-extensions-for-javascript" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#rxjs-reactive-extensions-for-javascript" aria-hidden="true">#</a> <img src="docs_app/src/assets/images/logos/Rx_Logo_S.png" alt="RxJS Logo" width="86" height="86"> RxJS: Reactive Extensions For JavaScript</h1>
<p><img src="https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/workflows/CI/badge.svg" alt="CI">
<a href="http://badge.fury.io/js/rxjs" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://badge.fury.io/js/rxjs.svg" alt="npm version"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a>
